The Word Explorer offers the following features:

Search for Words or Phrases: Scans files in a directory (including subdirectories) for a specific word or phrase.
Multithreading: Ensures fast and efficient processing by searching multiple files simultaneously.
Detailed Results:
File path
Line number
Position within the line
Line content
Customizable Options:
Case-sensitive or case-insensitive search.
Match whole words only.
Logging: Automatically saves all results to a log file.
File Skipping: Skips unreadable or non-text files.
User-Friendly Interface: Clear prompts and visual animations for a better user experience.
